<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV59">
<l>cālivēli taṇvayalta ṭaṅkiṭaṅku pūmpoḻil</l>
<l>kōlamāṭa nīṭutaṇku ṭantaimēya kōvalā</l>
<l>kālanēmi vakkaraṉka raṉmuraṉci rammavai</l>
<l>kālaṉōṭu kūṭaviṟku ṉittaviṟkai vīraṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Cowherd who joined the cool Kuṭantai with paddy fences, cool fields,</l>
<l>Wide moats, flowering groves, [and] tall, pretty mansions!</l>
<l>O Warrior with a bow in hand who bent the bow so that the heads of</l>
<l>Kālanemi, [Dantā]vakra, Khara, [and] Mura united with Death!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
